We work with lots of data from the reports of a cloud platform ours clients use to study languages, API endpoints of this platform already existing internal tools to manage contacts and relation with different organizations, a CRM to manage our students and a mass mailing platform.
We already interconnected all these services with no-code platforms but we are rebuilding our database so that it can be the source of professional internal tools in the form of a web interface.
We have extensive knowledge of the processes and of the data structure, we can already provide the design of the MongoDB database we are building and, after an initial meeting, we can provide you with a document with various instructions on the platform we want.
We need you to present us a solution for this, concerning the technology you suggest us to use (be it a a specific framework or a low-code internal tools builder) and to meet with us to start building the first steps and check if you are the right professional for us.
Our project can be split in the following steps, but we can explain in more details and provide you with a more organized document:
1) Interface with the MongoDB database;
2) Permission system to be able to create users for this platform and give them access to differente sections (the database we are building already has some, if not all, the fields that are needed to make such platform work);
3) Web interface to manage contacts and the licenses we provide to them for the study platform, with the possibility to show aggregated data from the database and select multiple contacts/licenses on which make operations (we also have to manage entire organizations and their namespaces in the study platform);
4) Connection layer to the API endpoints of the study platform we provide our clients with, so that we can manage their licenses or manage the namespaces of the organizations in the study platform;
5) Conncection layer to the API endoints of the mass mailing platform we use;
6) A logging system for the operations administration usres can perform;
7) Probably a long term objective, a system of automatization in the backend to manage contacts and licenses, send communications and reports, receive forms; all things we already implemented in a less professional way and that we can guide you through.<b>Skills</b>:        Web Application,                     Web Development,                     NoSQL Database

